{"about_the_game":"Did you know that 9 out 10 wildfires are caused by human activities? FireStarter 2 gives you the opportunity to start--virtually--one of them.<br><br>The idea of FireStarter 2 is to make players aware of the impact of forest fires on their environment.<br><br>While you can just watch the forest grow naturally through the years, you can also get involved in destructive or helpful ways.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Start a fire and see how it spreads and destroys your forest, only to watch it slowly reborn from the ashes.<br></li><li>Create clouds to decide where the rain should fall, but watch for thunderstorms when it's getting hot around.<br></li><li>Control rain to fight fire, or just to turn your dry plants green again.<br></li><li>Play with wind to control fire spread direction and clouds movement.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727071253","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059480/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727071253","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059480/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727071253","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059480/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727071253","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Did you know that 9 out 10 wildfires are caused by human activities? FireStarter 2 gives you the opportunity to start--virtually--one of them.<br><br>The idea of FireStarter 2 is to make players aware of the impact of forest fires on their environment.<br><br>While you can just watch the forest grow naturally through the years, you can also get involved in destructive or helpful ways.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Start a fire and see how it spreads and destroys your forest, only to watch it slowly reborn from the